{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cd25af777d","title":"邓小平就北京大学文化革命运动对女儿邓楠的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4ba576aa54","index":0,"year":1966,"month":6,"day":22,"articleId":"cd25af777d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f0e44655bb","name":"邓小平"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0da8a3846b","type":"title","text":"邓小平就北京大学文化革命运动对女儿邓楠的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"1dd90db3bb","type":"authors","text":"邓小平","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"edb705b00e","type":"paragraph","text":"1、放手发动群众，最后达到95％，打击面要小。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"3bce983f82","type":"paragraph","text":"2、排队，给老师、同学、左、中、右都排队。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"4ad442190b","type":"paragraph","text":"3、不断地扩大左派队伍，争取中间派，批落后分子、右派队伍。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"606af5c069","type":"paragraph","text":"4、工作队应该起个参谋作用，指出方向，出点子，想想办法，让学生自己去做。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"d47f64d599","type":"paragraph","text":"5、师生要挂勾，发动群众，让学生做老师的工作，让学生动动脑筋，培养学生分析问题研究问题的能力。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"bcbda01db3","type":"paragraph","text":"6、要文斗，不要武斗，打人是最容易的事，……给坏人造成混乱时机。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"60b31d8b60","type":"paragraph","text":"7、不打无准备之仗，哪怕晚几天都行，目标一定要选中、选对，要给各种人排队分类，揪出主要矛盾。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"216d7c1b1f","type":"paragraph","text":"材料要充分，要做各种各样的准备工作，加强调查研究，做各种人的工作等。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"1189c66515","type":"paragraph","text":"8、要沉得住气，不要着慌，要稳得住，顶得住。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"},{"id":"2e583d4aa1","type":"paragraph","text":"9、（因为女儿提出了下乡、下下厂、当兵。）想问题要想得全面，考虑问题要全面，要做当工农兵的准备，也要做掌握印把子、掌握政权的准备，要一颗红心多种准备，以党的需要为第一需要。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d"}],"page":{"id":"833bcf2f6f","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cd25af777d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}